<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="gravity-n">gravity <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɡrævəti/    美 /'ɡrævəti/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>重力；地心引力：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Newton's law of gravity
牛顿万有引力定律</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>严肃；庄重；严重性：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He spoke slowly and with great gravity.
他语速很慢，而且十分严肃。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don't think you realize the gravity of the situation.
我认为你没有意识到形势的严重性。</p></div></div>